565
00:42:39,023 --> 00:42:40,457
A handsome man.

566
00:42:40,691 --> 00:42:44,719
Issho naru means to sleep together.

567
00:42:44,996 --> 00:42:48,955
Iro otoko means a handsome man.

568
00:42:49,200 --> 00:42:51,760
Kirei onna. Come on.

569
00:42:52,003 --> 00:42:56,167
Kirei onna means a beautiful woman.

570
00:43:25,636 --> 00:43:28,367
The teacher is coming...

571
00:43:29,273 --> 00:43:31,264
Dad, the teacher is here.

572
00:43:32,276 --> 00:43:33,437
In 1898,

573
00:43:33,678 --> 00:43:35,305
the Japanese government turned

574
00:43:35,546 --> 00:43:36,809
Japanese centers
into six-year public schools

575
00:43:37,048 --> 00:43:40,279
offering a new form of education.

576
00:43:40,651 --> 00:43:43,177
But to Taiwanese families
at that time,

577
00:43:43,421 --> 00:43:44,286
since this new form of education

578
00:43:44,522 --> 00:43:46,547
no longer offered an imperial
examination system,

579
00:43:46,791 --> 00:43:49,658
they'd rather have
their children tend farming.

580
00:43:49,894 --> 00:43:51,988
So Japanese elementary
school teachers

581
00:43:52,230 --> 00:43:53,755
had to pay house calls

582
00:43:53,998 --> 00:43:55,295
to persuade parents

583
00:43:55,533 --> 00:43:57,365
to send their children to school.

584
00:44:05,343 --> 00:44:07,072
Good afternoon, everyone.

585
00:44:07,311 --> 00:44:11,043
Good afternoon, Teacher.

586
00:44:12,316 --> 00:44:13,784
After 1910,

587
00:44:14,018 --> 00:44:16,009
when the Japanese rule
became stable,

588
00:44:16,254 --> 00:44:17,983
Taiwanese families
were more willing

589
00:44:18,222 --> 00:44:21,192
to send their children
to these new schools.

590
00:44:21,425 --> 00:44:22,950
After six-year study
at the elementary school,

591
00:44:23,194 --> 00:44:26,357
some even attended vocational
or teacher's schools.

592
00:44:32,870 --> 00:44:34,133
The new education system

593
00:44:34,372 --> 00:44:35,771
unavoidably tried to instill ideas

594
00:44:36,007 --> 00:44:37,600
of Japan's greatness

595
00:44:37,842 --> 00:44:39,606
to attain the goal of
assimilating Taiwanese.

596
00:44:39,844 --> 00:44:41,642
It also provided common knowledge,

597
00:44:41,879 --> 00:44:43,608
and liberal arts courses,

598
00:44:43,848 --> 00:44:44,644
which developed the Taiwanese's

599
00:44:44,882 --> 00:44:47,249
scientific spirit and world views.

600
00:44:47,518 --> 00:44:50,010
It also built a strong foundation

601
00:44:50,254 --> 00:44:52,279
for the future cultural and
social reform movements.

602
00:45:21,986 --> 00:45:23,681
The Japanese Empire treated Taiwan,

603
00:45:23,955 --> 00:45:25,548
their first colony overseas,

604
00:45:25,790 --> 00:45:28,623
with benevolence and strictness.

605
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:31,725
Compared with the passivity
of the Qing Empire,

606
00:45:31,963 --> 00:45:33,931
this treatment was
far more aggressive.

607
00:45:34,098 --> 00:45:35,930
It was a totalitarian rule

608
00:45:36,100 --> 00:45:36,794
that opted to control the society

609
00:45:37,034 --> 00:45:39,696
from top to bottom.

610
00:45:40,137 --> 00:45:40,831
The various forces

611
00:45:41,072 --> 00:45:42,801
that had existed in local communities

612
00:45:43,040 --> 00:45:45,134
were consequently demolished.

613
00:45:50,982 --> 00:45:52,006
Taiwan was a pre-modern society

614
00:45:52,250 --> 00:45:54,480
that was lax and closed off.

615
00:45:54,719 --> 00:45:56,380
But under the Japanese rule,

616
00:45:56,621 --> 00:45:58,817
It gradually became

617
00:45:59,056 --> 00:46:01,991
a coherent and modern society.

618
00:46:03,995 --> 00:46:05,053
In 1919,

619
00:46:05,296 --> 00:46:08,163
the Japanese government carried out

620
00:46:08,399 --> 00:46:09,560
“ Japanese extensionism, ”
an assimilation policy,

621
00:46:09,800 --> 00:46:11,700
which would turn Taiwan
into a part of Japan,

622
00:46:11,936 --> 00:46:14,371
and would treat it as equally
as Japan proper.

623
00:46:14,672 --> 00:46:16,401
That year, the Office
of Governor-General,

624
00:46:16,641 --> 00:46:18,666
the highest Japanese government
institution

625
00:46:18,943 --> 00:46:20,240
in Taiwan, was completed.

626
00:46:20,478 --> 00:46:21,912
The Japanese rule of Taiwan

627
00:46:22,079 --> 00:46:24,673
reached a stable stage.

